ope; in the Class I stage, the outflow enters the momentum-driven\nsnow-plough phase. Our results suggest that protostellar outflow should\ndetermine the final stellar mass and significantly affect the early evolution\nof low-mass protostars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Feb 2013 07:59:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
