olliders as Tevatron and LHC,\nsuch a super $Z$-factory will present an excellent platform for studying the\nheavy quarkonium properties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Feb 2013 14:18:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 25 Apr 2013 12:14:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 23 May 2013 03:10:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-06-10"}
